Class Report

java.lang.Object
com.panotify.model.Report
public class Report extends Object
Represents a summary report of a student's exam attempt. Contains scores, status, timing, and display information for reporting.

    • Report

      public Report()
      Default constructor for Report class. Sets startedAt to now and status to "in_progress".

    • Report

      public Report(int studentId, int examId, int totalScore, int maxScore)
      Constructs a new Report with the specified details. Sets startedAt and submittedAt to now and status to "completed".
      Parameters:
      studentId - The ID of the student
      examId - The ID of the exam
      totalScore - The total score achieved
      maxScore - The maximum possible score
